    public static interface AsyncTransactionManager.TransactionContextFuture
extends com.google.api.core.ApiFuture<TransactionContext>

        Sets the first step to execute as part of this transaction after the transaction has started using the specified executor. MoreExecutors.directExecutor() can be be used for lightweight functions, but should be avoided for heavy or blocking operations.
